{"tid":1057569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［侏羅紀公園］日本有望讓滅絕了約1萬年的長毛象復活","createTime":"2019-03-12T03:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T03:55:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c318cc7bd44c5df5866db7c33f050a079b1e1d7c","tid":1057569,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"日本近畿大學講師宮本圭等人組成的研究團隊3月11日宣佈，成功使從長毛象化石提取出的細胞核在老鼠的卵子內實現再生。研究團隊提取出在西伯利亞發現的長毛象的肌肉組織，進行了實證實驗。未來有望使已經滅絕的長毛象復活。這一成果于11日發佈在英國科學雜誌《科學報告》的電子版上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/12/113042_27debdc28782e0681a5eca6fc005c3bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F113042_27debdc28782e0681a5eca6fc005c3bc.png&h=5575b26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雌性長毛象YUKA的化石（近畿大學，kyodo）<br />\n       研究團隊從在西伯利亞的永凍層沉睡了2.8萬年的長毛象「YUKA」體內提取出骨髓和肌肉組織。將遺傳信息與非洲象進行比較，確認到長毛象特有的DNA和蛋白質。<br />\n<br />\n       團隊從肌肉組織中提取細胞核成分，移植到老鼠的卵子中，結果細胞成長至分裂前的狀態。此外還略微出現了長毛象DNA中損傷的部分獲得修復的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yELDZX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yELDZX.png&h=5925eb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n       宮本強調，「希望未來能進展到細胞分裂。朝著復活長毛象的目標邁出了有意義的一步」。不過他同時表示，復活長毛象「還需要一些時間」。<br />\n<br />\n       近畿大學成立了復活長毛象的項目並推進研究，力爭通過「體細胞核移植」的克隆技術復活被認為在約1萬年前滅絕的長毛象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/34671-2019-03-12-10-19-18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Fscienceatechnology%2F34671-2019-03-12-10-19-18.html&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6JFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=5efa3b52\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/34671-2019-03-12-10-19-18.html</a>"},{"pid":"cd92526b42b1be51c701f5423da78aa4444f2d06","tid":1057569,"uid":83251,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"日本科研<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dd9cbbf8e5e8395fc4ee7a2c040bc316106b71","tid":1057569,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"但會唔會適認唔到現今嘅環境(天氣/食物)就好快死"},{"pid":"69592cc7264bf091d516fa30d2d95371b2d23f6e","tid":1057569,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76dd9cbbf8e5e8395fc4ee7a2c040bc316106b71","tid":1057569,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"但會唔會適認唔到現今嘅環境(天氣/食物)就好快死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"圈養咪得"},{"pid":"79641e7bfe8576d5689b0e8a62048bd99bad0b8a","tid":1057569,"uid":59041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"屌呢日新聞前幾年已經有，幾時先真係複製到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e713e11e5c26c18afc479ba6acf714d8559916","tid":1057569,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69592cc7264bf091d516fa30d2d95371b2d23f6e","tid":1057569,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76dd9cbbf8e5e8395fc4ee7a2c040bc316106b71","tid":1057569,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"但會唔會適認唔到現今嘅環境(天氣/食物)就好快死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"圈養咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"然後啲動保撚又屌用溫室用人工嘢用乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473e822a95865955c51e1d7842c9a4f619c42663","tid":1057569,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76dd9cbbf8e5e8395fc4ee7a2c040bc316106b71","tid":1057569,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"但會唔會適認唔到現今嘅環境(天氣/食物)就好快死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"繁殖一百隻出嚟做實驗測試適合氣候 仲可以準確推斷到當時大氣結構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}